Sentence: Yoshinobu Ōga (大賀 好修, Ōga Yoshinobu) is a Japanese musical arranger and guitarist in distributors Being Inc., mainly in their label Giza Studio.
In years 2000-2002 he was part of the Japanese soul band Nothin' but love, in years 2004-2009 part of Japanese pop band OOM and since 2012 he's member of fusion band Sensation as a guitarist.
